{"tid":1122262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【諜戰】美起訴兩華人助中國竊取GE機密","createTime":"2019-04-24T00:19:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T06:47:38.000Z","uid":54733,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b19c71e8b620f37b2d7b6eb78ae98bc526a1dc2d","tid":1122262,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T00:19:29.000Z","msg":"【Now財經台】美國起訴兩名華人竊取通用電氣(GE)商業機密。<br />\n<br />\n據美國司法部的起訴書顯示，通用電氣前工程師鄭曉青及一名中國商人，被控從事經濟間諜活動，合謀竊取通用電氣商業機密令中國得益，兩人被控14項罪名，並於上周四被正式起訴，起訴書指出，兩人透過自通用電氣竊取的訊息，在遼寧天翼航空科技及南京天翼航空科技兩家渦輪機研發公司，為個人謀取商業利益。<br />\n<br />\n此外，起訴書又補充，兩人透過這兩家公司，獲得中國政府在經濟及其他範疇的支持，並跟中國政府官員進行協調。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.now.com/mobile/news/article/502156\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F502156&d=zdm3SfM4sEUVnXmiquxubA5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=c0bd72f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://finance.now.com/mobile/news/article/502156</a>"},{"pid":"d79031b3c1125ada22482550e38947f4fa39b628","tid":1122262,"uid":81113,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T00:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HSroXvk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHSroXvk.png&h=4125b325&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9d7805a1985b3fccbb246670b87a7658ae9441d","tid":1122262,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T00:24:28.000Z","msg":"有排捉 放左咁多入嚟"},{"pid":"0ffaa5e0df7bebfcfab7494e4142a27d8d1e49e7","tid":1122262,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d79031b3c1125ada22482550e38947f4fa39b628","tid":1122262,"uid":81113,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T00:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HSroXvk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHSroXvk.png&h=4125b325&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T01:07:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\"